{"tid":2064883,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬交] 澳門政府聽日開始，對上年有交過稅嘅打工仔每人派萬五","createTime":"2020-06-15T06:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T07:33:11.000Z","uid":154872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8963af4efdf97217d6870e9b5ed420ebe6f069","tid":2064883,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"退稅額唔過兩萬的話<br />\n<br />\n就每個打工仔派萬五（仲自動轉帳）"},{"pid":"9e591136a5fe1d8814a4507491a71e06da667f97","tid":2064883,"uid":17799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"冇返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776b764346727185507e87e227b5ae1543ac516a","tid":2064883,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"援助款項發放金額為15,000元，發放條件為：<br />\n<br />\n(1)於2020年3月31日持有有效或可續期的澳門居民身份證；<br />\n(2)於2019年1月1日至2020年3月31日期間有任何任職記錄，且須最遲於2020年3月31日申報入職M/2；<br />\n(3)2018年度職業稅退稅計劃中退稅金額未達20,000元。<br />\n<br />\n下列情況者不符合發放資格：<br />\n<br />\n(1)公職人員；<br />\n(2)其僱主未於法定期限內遞交2017年度至2019年度職業稅M3/M4僱員或散工名表以申報僱員收益；<br />\n(3)其僱主於2017年度至2019年度職業稅M3/M4僱員或散工名表上申報該僱員沒有任何職業稅收益；<br />\n(4)依法獲豁免繳納職業稅，但其2018年度職業稅可課稅收益對應可獲的退稅金額達20,000元的人士。"},{"pid":"8be55a9ec45f6aaf3ed11160e975fa8f01c2cd0b","tid":2064883,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8963af4efdf97217d6870e9b5ed420ebe6f069","tid":2064883,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"退稅額唔過兩萬的話<br />\n<br />\n就每個打工仔派萬五（仲自動轉帳）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:33:45.000Z","msg":"Fatfat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6588084d17a1ed7d7fe548b8fec260a8fbe99","tid":2064883,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be55a9ec45f6aaf3ed11160e975fa8f01c2cd0b","tid":2064883,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8963af4ef